Package: FormIOr
Title: Download, Clean, and Export FormIO Submissions
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rodrigo", "Solis Sosa", email = "dr.rodrigo.solis@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for downloading FormIO submissions (responses), flattening
    nested structures, cleaning and simplifying repeated and multi-select
    answers, generating diagnostics (codebooks, summaries, plots), maintaining
    audit logs of dataset processing, and exporting results to Excel or
    delimited files. Includes an interactive end-to-end workflow for
    non-technical users.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ORG/FormIOr
BugReports: https://github.com/ORG/FormIOr/issues
